<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.1.3">
<l>vāṉāṭum maṇṇāṭum maṟṟuḷḷa palluyirum</l>
<l>tāṉāya vemperumāṉ talaivaṉamarn tuṟaiyumiṭam</l>
<l>āṉāta peruñcelvat tarumaṟaiyōr nāṅkaitaṉṉuḷ</l>
<l>tēṉāru malarpoḻilcūḻ tiruttēva ṉārtokaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where serenely dwells our great lord [and] leader as himself,</l>
<l>And as the many beings which are in the heavenly realm, the earthly realm,</l>
<l rend="indent">and other [realms],</l>
<l>Is Tiruttēvaṉārtokai, girded by groves with honey-filled flowers,</l>
<l>In Nāṅkai with experts in the rare Vedas</l>
<l rend="indent">of inexhaustible great [wealth of] learning.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
